- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with extracting interpretable content from unstructured data.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses deep neural network text-embedding methodologies.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with healthcare records and has implications for healthcare providers and patients.
